36:24.000 --> 36:27.000
Or we can use money

36:27.000 --> 36:29.000
to quantify

36:29.000 --> 36:31.000
almost everything in the world

36:31.000 --> 36:34.000
in a system of communication.

36:34.000 --> 36:37.000
This is the second thing I think

36:37.000 --> 36:41.000
that eco-scientists are facing now.

36:41.000 --> 36:44.000
This is also a problem

36:44.000 --> 36:46.000
that some scholars

36:46.000 --> 36:49.000
who are not trained in ecology

36:49.000 --> 36:53.000
want to help us solve.

36:53.000 --> 36:56.000
How to quantify ecosystem services,

36:56.000 --> 36:58.000
especially these services

36:58.000 --> 37:02.000
related to culture.

37:02.000 --> 37:04.000
Even when I was at this conference,

